FBIS3-7335 "dreas059_c_94003" FBIS-EAS-94-059 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Mar 1994 North Korea Spokesmen's Statements Entered in UNSC Record Foreign Ministry Spokesman OW2803053694 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0515 GMT 28 Mar 94 OW2803053694 Pyongyang KCNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Pyongyang, March 28 (KCNA) -- The March 21 statement of a spokesman for the Foreign Ministry of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea denouncing the United States for its perfidious act in totally reversing the February 25 agreed conclusions reached at the DPRK-U.S. contact in New York was distributed on March 22 as an official document S/1994/327 of the United Nations Security Council.
